<h3>Action Menu</h3>
<p>Actions for single entry, invoked using the Action link (gear icon).</p>
<ol>
  <li>User clicks gear icon.</li>
  <li>Action menu slides into view beneath primary/secondary navigation.</li>
  <li>Displays article actions for: Watching the article, editing visibility settings.</li>
</ol>
<h3>Shared Folders</h3>
<p>Shared folders menu, moved from Mexico tools.</p>
<ol>
  <li>Shared folders tab appears next to attachments</li>
  <li>If user selects shared folder tab, an input will appear to allow the user to add new folders.</li>
  <li>When new folders are added, the user may click the folder name to open the folder contents in place. A link will appear below each open folder to upload new files into it.</li>
</ol> 